name: webinarPanelistsDelete
description:
Remove all the panelists from a Webinar.
**Scopes:** `webinar:write:admin` `webinar:write`
**[Rate Limit Label](https://marketplace.zoom.us/docs/api-reference/rate-limits#rate-limits):** `Light`
**Prerequisites:**
* Pro or a higher plan with [Webinar Add-on](https://zoom.us/webinar).

webinarId.description: The webinar ID in "**long**" format(represented as int64 data type in JSON).
